      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical health is prioritized, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and documented rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Power is delivered to the asphalt via a factory limited-slip differential, and the suspension geometry remains true for precise turn-in. While showing minor road patina, the chassis is tight and the powertrain pulls strong to the 8,000 RPM redline. An exceptional balance of analog feedback and mechanical integrity for the serious enthusiast.",
